title Ex0.6: Single page app form


note over Browser:
User Enters information in the form
and clicks the save button
end note

note over Browser:
using JavaScript preventDefault() method
to prevent the default action of the submit button (the form)
end note
Browser->Server: AJAX (POST) request https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/data.json
Server-->Browser: JSON data
note over Browser:
the browser executes an event handler
that renders the notes to display
end note
